name: DMLOST2.WAD
description: This is the Lost Level of DOOM, the one your mother never told you about! A big, complex WAD, almost 200K, this one is not for novices. NOTE: This is an updated version of The Lost Level of DOOM, using DEU 5.21 to align all the textures correctly, and fix a few minor bugs. Current as of June 25, 1994.
